---- MODULE DekkersAlgorithm ----
EXTENDS Integers, Sequences, FiniteSets

VARIABLES turn, wants

Init == /\ turn \in {0,1}
        /\ wants \in {0,1} \cup {0,1} \cup {0,1} \cup {0,1}
        /\ wants = [i \in {0,1} |-> 0]

Next == /\ turn' \in {0,1}
        /\ wants' \in {0,1} \cup {0,1} \cup {0,1} \cup {0,1}
        /\ turn' = turn
        /\ wants' = [i \in {0,1} |-> IF i = 0 THEN wants[0] ELSE IF i = 1 THEN wants[1] ELSE 0]

Spec == Init /\ [][Next]_<<turn, wants>>

